---
layout: base
---
<section class="hero">
  <div class="wrapper">
    <header class="gap-12 mb-24">
      <span class="hero__badge">Serviço</span>
      <h1 class="mb-4 font-extrabold text-6xl md:text-8xl leading-tight tracking-tighter hero__title">
        {{ title }}
      </h1>
      <p class="max-w-3xl text-text-muted text-xl md:text-3xl leading-relaxed hero__description">{{ service.tagline }}
      </p>
    </header>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark/50 py-20">
  <div class="mx-auto px-6 max-w-[800px]">
    <div class="mb-12 text-center">
      <span class="font-bold text-primary text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">O que é o serviço</span>
      <h2 class="mt-4 font-bold text-3xl tracking-tight">Transforme barreiras em oportunidades</h2>
    </div>
    <p class="mb-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 text-lg text-center leading-relaxed">
      Uma consultoria detalhada que analisa seu produto digital sob a ótica das diretrizes internacionais <strong>WCAG
        (Web Content Accessibility Guidelines)</strong>.
    </p>
    <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 text-lg text-center leading-relaxed">
      Ajudamos sua empresa a remover barreiras de interação e a transformar a acessibilidade em um diferencial
      competitivo, garantindo que ninguém seja deixado para trás na sua jornada digital.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="gap-16 grid md:grid-cols-2 mx-auto px-6 py-24 max-w-[1200px]">
  <div>
    <h3 class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8 font-bold text-2xl">
      <span class="text-primary material-symbols-outlined">check_circle</span>
      O que está incluído
    </h3>
    <ul class="space-y-6">
      <li class="flex gap-4">
        <span class="text-green-500 shrink-0 material-symbols-outlined">done</span>
        <div>
          <p class="font-bold text-[#141018] dark:text-white">Auditoria Completa WCAG 2.1/2.2</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">Avaliação detalhada nos níveis A e AA para garantir
            conformidade técnica.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="flex gap-4">
        <span class="text-green-500 shrink-0 material-symbols-outlined">done</span>
        <div>
          <p class="font-bold text-[#141018] dark:text-white">Testes com Tecnologias Assistivas</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">Verificação com leitores de tela (NVDA, JAWS, VoiceOver),
            navegação por teclado e comandos de voz.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="flex gap-4">
        <span class="text-green-500 shrink-0 material-symbols-outlined">done</span>
        <div>
          <p class="font-bold text-[#141018] dark:text-white">Relatório de Melhorias Priorizadas</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">Documentação técnica com bugs encontrados, impacto no
            usuário e sugestões de código para correção.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="flex gap-4">
        <span class="text-green-500 shrink-0 material-symbols-outlined">done</span>
        <div>
          <p class="font-bold text-[#141018] dark:text-white">Workshop de Handover</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">Sessão dedicada com seu time de engenharia e produto para
            explicar as vulnerabilidades encontradas.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div>
    <h3 class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8 font-bold text-2xl">
      <span class="text-primary material-symbols-outlined">account_tree</span>
      Nossa Metodologia
    </h3>
    <div class="relative space-y-12 ml-4 border-primary/20 border-l-2">
      <div class="relative pl-10">
        <span
          class="top-0 -left-3.25 absolute bg-primary border-4 border-white dark:border-background-dark rounded-full size-6"></span>
        <h4 class="mb-2 font-bold text-lg">1. Diagnóstico Automatizado</h4>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">Uso de ferramentas avançadas para identificação rápida de
          erros estruturais e de contraste em larga escala.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="relative pl-10">
        <span
          class="top-0 -left-2.25 absolute bg-primary border-4 border-white dark:border-background-dark rounded-full size-6"></span>
        <h4 class="mb-2 font-bold text-lg">2. Validação Manual</h4>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">Especialistas testam cada fluxo crítico para garantir que a
          lógica e o contexto estão acessíveis.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="relative pl-10">
        <span
          class="top-0 -left-3.25 absolute bg-primary border-4 border-white dark:border-background-dark rounded-full size-6"></span>
        <h4 class="mb-2 font-bold text-lg">3. Entrega de Roadmap</h4>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">Classificação de erros por severidade, facilitando o
          planejamento do seu backlog de correções.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Problem / Solution -->
<section class="bg-background-light py-20" aria-labelledby="problem-solution">
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="gap-6 grid md:grid-cols-2">
      <article class="box">
        <h2 class="mb-4 font-bold text-2xl" id="problem-solution">O problema</h2>
        <p class="text-muted">{{ service.problem | safe | nl2br }}</p>
      </article>

      <article class="box">
        <h2 class="mb-4 font-bold text-2xl">A solução</h2>
        <p class="text-muted">{{ service.solution | safe | nl2br }}</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Differentials -->
{% if service.differentials %}
<section class="region" aria-labelledby="differentials">
  <div class="wrapper">
    <h2 class="mb-4 font-extrabold text-4xl leading-tight hero__title" id="differentials">Por que essa avaliação é
      diferente</h2>
    <ul class="grid" data-layout="50-50" role="list">
      {% for item in service.differentials %}
      <li class="box">{{ item }}</li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>
{% endif %}

<!-- Included -->
{% if service.included %}
<section class="region" aria-labelledby="included">
  <div class="wrapper flow">
    <h2 class="text-center title" id="included">O que você recebe</h2>
    <ul class="gap-6 grid md:grid-cols-3">
      {% for item in service.included %}
      <li class="box">
        <div class="p-3 border rounded h-100">
          {{ item }}
        </div>
      </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
</section>
{% endif %}

<!-- Results -->
{% if service.results %}
<section class="region" aria-labelledby="results">
  <div class="wrapper flow">
    <h2 class="title" id="results">Resultados esperados</h2>
    <ul class="grid" data-layout="thirds" role="list">
      {% for result in service.results %}
      <li class="shadow card">
        <h3 class="h6 fw-bold">{{ result.title }}</h3>
        <p class="mb-0 text-muted">{{ result.description }}</p>
      </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
</section>
{% endif %}

<!-- Target -->
{% if service.target %}
<section class="region" aria-labelledby="target">
  <div class="wrapper flow">
    <h2 class="title" id="target">Para quem é indicado</h2>
    <ul class="grid" data-layout="thirds" role="list">
      {% for item in service.target %}
      <li class="box">
        {{ item }}
      </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
</section>
{% endif %}

<!-- Plans -->
{% if service.plans %}
{% set plansTitle = "Planos disponíveis" %}
{% set plans = service.plans %}
{% include "components/plans/plans-grid.njk" %}
{% endif %}

<!-- Process -->
{% if service.processes %}
<section class="region" aria-labelledby="process">
  <div class="wrapper flow">
    <h2 class="text-center title" id="process">Como funciona</h2>
    <ol class="grid" data-layout="50-50" role="list">
      {% for step in service.processes %}
      <li class="box">
        <strong>{{ step.title }}:</strong>
        <span class="text-muted">{{ step.description }}</span>
      </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ol>
  </div>
</section>
{% endif %}

<!-- Testimonial -->
{% if service.testimonials %}
<section class="region" aria-labelledby="testimonial">
  <div class="wrapper flow">
    <h2 class="text-center title" id="process">Depoimentos</h2>

    <div class="grid" data-layout="thirds">
      {% set testimonials = service.testimonials %}
      {% for testimonial in testimonials %}
      <blockquote class="box">
        <p class="mb-2">“{{ testimonial.quote }}”</p>
        <footer class="blockquote-footer">
          {{ testimonial.client }}
        </footer>
      </blockquote>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
</section>
{% endif %}

<!-- FAQ -->
{% if service.faq %}
<section class="py-20" aria-labelledby="faq">
  <div class="wrapper flow">
    <h2 class="mb-4 font-extrabold text-4xl text-center leading-tight hero__title title" id="faq">Perguntas frequentes</h2>

    <div class="mx-auto max-7xl" data-layout="50-50">
      {% for item in service.faq %}
      <details class="box accordion-item">
        <summary class="accordion-header">{{ item.question }}</summary>
        <p>{{ item.answer }}</p>
      </details>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
{% endif %}

<!-- CTA -->
{% set cta = service.cta %}
{% include "components/cta/cta-block.njk" %}